==Biggest victories and losses==

* Biggest win: 14–0 v. CPD Gwalchmai in 2013
* Biggest defeat: 0–12 v. Everton Reserves in the 1930s.
* Biggest League of Wales win: 9–0 v. [[Haverfordwest County A.F.C.|Haverfordwest County]] in 1994.
* Biggest League of Wales defeat: 1–9 v. [[The New Saints F.C.|The New Saints]] in 2014.
* Biggest European Competition win: 2–0 v. [[S.S.C. Napoli|Napoli]], 5 September 1962.
* Biggest European Competition defeat: 0–10 v. [[HJK Helsinki]], 19 July 2011.

